{
  "stem": "1020.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you don't practice, if you don't speak-- but I will read a letter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will understand the language very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What other languages do you speak?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I speak the English language, Yiddish, Polish, German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I do get into Hebrew, but I don't speak Hebrew well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never had the chance to-- Hebrew doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--settled in in the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And every camp had a police force, but not, you know, with ammunition, with guns-- security, for security reasons.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, as I was a-- an army man discharged from an army, they were looking for it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was already in Germany and in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was recorded into the Berihah-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] into the Berihah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We smuggled out children from Germany into Italy, and then to Palestine--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Jewish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was recorded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was on the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went on night duty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got to come to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll tell you what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We decided, me and Anni, to get married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We lived in one room, two sisters and myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had a dream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother came to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I told you, it was-- and she told me, it's not right to live with women like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's not our belief-- in a dream.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I talked to Anni.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I decided, are we getting married?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If not, you go your way, I go my way, I says.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, two girls and-- with me together in a home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had their bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had my bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the camp treated us very well, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we get a-- February, we got married.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
